Type SyntaxTransformerFunction is Function that takes ast as ASTNode and context as Dictionary[String, Any] returns ASTNode

Type SyntaxRewriterFunction is Function that takes ast as ASTNode and rules as List[RewriteRule] returns ASTNode

Type SyntaxNormalizerFunction is Function that takes ast as ASTNode and normalization as NormalizationSpec returns ASTNode

Type SyntaxValidatorFunction is Function that takes ast as ASTNode returns ValidationResult

Type SyntaxCheckerFunction is Function that takes ast as ASTNode returns CheckResult

Type SyntaxVerifierFunction is Function that takes ast as ASTNode returns VerificationResult

